THE SCHOLARS STRATEGY NETWORK (SSN) PROVIDES FREE EDUCATIONAL INFORMATION TO THE PUBLIC ON AN ONGOING BASIS, THROUGH PODCAST, SOCIAL MEDIA POSTS, AND THROUGH A WEB-BASED LIBRARY OF RESEARCH BRIEFS, WHICH IS SSN'S LARGEST INTELLECTUAL ASSET. THE PURPOSE OF THE GRANT, REPRODUCTIVE JUSTICE: CONNECTING REPRODUCTIVE HEALTH SCHOLARS TO THE PUBLIC, THE MEDIA, POLICYMAKERS, AND OTHER SCHOLARS, WAS SOLELY TO FURTHER SSN'S EXEMPT CHARITABLE MISSION. SSN IS MAKING SUBSTANTIAL EFFORTS TO ATTRACT ADDITIONAL AND NEW PUBLIC FUNDING BY REACHING OUT TO INDIVIDUALS AT LEVELS THAT WILL PLACE MOST OF THEIR GIFTS WELL WITHIN THE PUBLIC SUPPORT MARK, AND BY REACHING OUT TO PUBLIC CHARITIES, SUCH AS COMMUNITY FOUNDATIONS, FOR SUPPORT. WE EXPECT THESE ENDEAVORS WILL RESTORE SSN'S PUBLIC SUPPORT WELL ABOVE THE ONE THIRD MARK IN THE FUTURE.
